Compile the wrapper and the demos:
make all

Just compile the wrapper:
make lib

Use it:
LD_PRELOAD=./glQuadBufferEmu.so YourQuadBufferedApplication

Example of use: 
LD_PRELOAD=./glQuadBufferEmu.so glxgears -stereo

